{"tid":1755141,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"非泛民要用公費請核數師, 核對去年區議會的數","createTime":"2019-11-25T12:45:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T04:59:58.000Z","uid":76310,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"99c7b0ddd36639578ec123581b046d1a184970d2","tid":1755141,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T12:45:13.000Z","msg":"非泛民要用公費請核數師, 核對去年區議會的數<br />\n有沒有利益衝突, 有沒有利益輸送, 有沒有私相授受, 有沒有不清楚的數?<br />\n如果有任何證據發現不妥, 例如貪污, 利益輸送, 利益衝突<br />\n開記者招待會, 向各界交待當中的問題, 另外向icac要求作出起數(當然我明白icac都是正苦的, 但就是向icac施, 如果他們不核查, 讓人知道正苦包庇奶共派)<br />\n刑事也好, 民事也好, 用公帑向奶共派清數, 奶共派勾結和利益輸送到出晒面, 幾乎必中<br />\n不單可以令全世界知道奶共派既仆街, 而且可以向他們清算<br />\n這招是民進黨向國民黨清算的方法"},{"pid":"da68ca0601863ded53d319c9f794a96d3536036a","tid":1755141,"uid":5549,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T12:46:18.000Z","msg":"蕭生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52c4021f0d01bbc7848b201915d9d24a8f8fea42","tid":1755141,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T12:46:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"27372c66b3b3a417b202a77c08f60cf3246cd291","tid":1755141,"uid":114447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T12:47:21.000Z","msg":"big4 有邊個partner 唔係奶共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba08f58dae7177dfd824281095612d9a4b58bd6c","tid":1755141,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T12:47:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fee4fad1083552dd3b8191184f61e37774636f84","tid":1755141,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T12:48:01.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6854d088fd85519efb4dc2bd22c2977b37dbfb1a","tid":1755141,"uid":85327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T12:48:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e1353747fe5